data.description: WOW! Seller will provide up to $5,000.00 towards BUYER's closing costs or use to buy down interest rate!! Serene country living in this 3BR, 2BA haven on a spacious 2-acre corner lot. Embrace the warmth of the WBFP in the open living area, flowing seamlessly into a modern kitchen with decorative lighting, SS appliances, double oven, and a breakfast nook. Reverse osmosis and water softener! Indulge in the luxurious master ensuite, featuring a freestanding soaking tub, dual sinks, and a large walk-in closet . Landscaped yard with sprinklers. Head to the MOVIES! Study has been thoughtfully transformed into a versatile MEDIA room, providing a dedicated space for movie nights, gaming, or even a home office. PEASTER ISD. Just a short drive away from downtown Weatherford and I-20, offering easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options.
